00:32:25,995 --> 00:32:26,955
Even the one we thought

287
00:32:27,035 --> 00:32:28,755
would always spoil her is gone.

288
00:32:29,675 --> 00:32:32,275
How much longer can we accompany her?

289
00:32:35,394 --> 00:32:36,475
If, one day,

290
00:32:36,955 --> 00:32:37,995
we are no longer here,

291
00:32:39,715 --> 00:32:40,874
