this delicious before.

306
00:34:55,955 --> 00:34:57,074
The noodles are soft

307
00:34:58,194 --> 00:34:59,074
yet not mushy.

308
00:35:01,795 --> 00:35:03,554
The first time Jinzhao cooked noodles,

309
00:35:04,355 --> 00:35:05,754
he cooked them for so long

310
00:35:06,554 --> 00:35:08,194
