311
00:35:09,395 --> 00:35:10,955
Later, when he cooked noodles,

312
00:35:11,955 --> 00:35:13,194
they were always undercooked.

313
00:35:17,835 --> 00:35:19,274
And the vegetable leaves are green.

314
00:35:23,114 --> 00:35:24,475
The noodles Jinzhao cooked for me

315
00:35:25,234 --> 00:35:27,274
had yellow vegetable leaves in them.

316
00:35:28,714 --> 00:35:30,395
I said they wouldn't taste good
like that.

317
00:35:32,035 --> 00:35:33,674
The next time he served me noodles,

318
00:35:34,554 --> 00:35:37,355
