blanched the vegetable leaves.

319
00:35:43,435 --> 00:35:45,114
This egg is still runny in the center.

320
00:35:47,835 --> 00:35:49,915
This is my favorite way to eat eggs.

321
00:35:51,995 --> 00:35:54,114
But Jinzhao never cooked them
like this for me.

322
00:35:54,915 --> 00:35:55,714
He said

323
00:35:56,475 --> 00:35:57,915
