it'd give me a stomach ache.

324
00:36:00,355 --> 00:36:02,194
I think he just didn't know
how to cook them.

325
00:36:20,594 --> 00:36:21,395
What's wrong?

326
00:36:25,274 --> 00:36:26,035
Nothing.

327
00:36:26,515 --> 00:36:28,714
I just ate too quickly.

328
00:36:28,995 --> 00:36:30,194
I feel a bit uncomfortable.

329
00:36:30,915 --> 00:36:31,714
Then stop eating them.

330
00:36:31,714 --> 00:36:32,315
No.

331
00:36:32,915 --> 00:36:34,915
Jinzhao told me not to waste food.

332
00:36:42,114 --> 00:36:43,074
They are really delicious.

333
00:36:50,074 --> 00:36:50,835
I've finished.

334
00:36:53,475 --> 00:36:55,274
