on the corner of your mouth.

335
00:37:01,154 --> 00:37:02,714
On the left corner.

336
00:37:07,262 --> 00:37:10,392
♪Unfelt sensations♪

337
00:37:10,904 --> 00:37:14,198
♪What seemed eternal♪

338
00:37:14,462 --> 00:37:19,654
