overflow into tears♪

346
00:37:45,594 --> 00:37:46,554
It means that person

347
00:37:49,194 --> 00:37:50,634
is gone forever.

348
00:37:56,315 --> 00:37:57,995
When Shifang died,

349
00:37:59,875 --> 00:38:02,234
