in my heart.

350
00:38:04,995 --> 00:38:06,754
After Zhu Yu fell asleep,

351
00:38:08,714 --> 00:38:11,274
I felt the hole in my heart
grow even larger.

352
00:38:13,795 --> 00:38:14,995
But now,

353
00:38:16,995 --> 00:38:20,074
