I don't even have a heart anymore.

354
00:38:23,280 --> 00:38:26,213
♪Vows are said to burn to ash♪

355
00:38:29,114 --> 00:38:31,875
He would never call me a fool again.

356
00:38:32,594 --> 00:38:35,234
He would never pat me on the head

357
00:38:36,515 --> 00:38:39,194
or call me Qi again.

358
00:38:41,355 --> 00:38:42,795
If you're sad, just have a good cry.

359
00:38:46,114 --> 00:38:47,515
Jinzhao is no longer here.

360
00:38:48,634 --> 00:38:50,435
