364
00:39:18,795 --> 00:39:20,074
I'm not crying anymore.

365
00:39:28,194 --> 00:39:30,315
Thank you for celebrating my birthday.

366
00:39:31,754 --> 00:39:32,515
These past few days,

367
00:39:33,515 --> 00:39:34,915
I have caused you trouble.

368
00:39:38,114 --> 00:39:39,634
You two should rest first.

369
00:39:40,915 --> 00:39:42,274
I'm going to see Ying Xuwei.

370
00:39:57,554 --> 00:39:58,274
She should

371
00:40:00,435 --> 00:40:02,515
